casebody.data:
Foerster et al. v. Gallinger et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by William Foerster and others against Joseph Gallinger and another

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion denied. See 17 N. Y. Supp. 144.
